{"tid":550781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【你收唔收？】Dior狗年利是封咁嘅樣 網友「駡」聲四起","createTime":"2018-02-05T05:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T03:07:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":585,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"50dd6f927db21ffc3f3ab7d1751d5cf45518655a","tid":550781,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180205/large/1517800317_71a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180205%2Flarge%2F1517800317_71a6.jpg&h=3da216c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗年要來了，各大名牌愛吹中國風，紛紛推出有關「狗」的貨品。近日，有內地網民Po出今年Christian Dior的利是封，紅色的利是封上只印了一個金色的「狗」字，網友揶揄是罵人神器，若見到這樣的紅包「你收不收？」。<br />\n<br />\n微博網友@Irissiel昨天Po出了一個Dior為了中國新年設計的利是封，並寫道：「迪奧（Dior）為了中國新年準備的紅包。今天最好笑的笑話」；網友紛紛回應：「這個紅包，簡直是無形中的罵人神器啊！錢送了，人也罵了&hellip;&hellip;」；另有網友說：「專門給單身狗」；「這簡宜就是無形中的駡人神器」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180205/57794056\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F57794056&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=560830cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F57794056&h=6f4985fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180205/57794056</a>"},{"pid":"56a94015a0564b6570077ff1d441cb0c0fb8888e","tid":550781,"uid":90,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99074d4863c75a0f96ef0356b37ac1439eb2e74c","tid":550781,"uid":52215,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"